                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The destrachan emits a sonic cry in either a @Template[type:cone|distance:60] or a @Template[type:burst|distance:30]. This discordant ululation resonates along the nerves and bones of living creatures in the area, manifesting as waves of incapacitating pain washing over the victims. Each living creature in the area must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:26] save.</p>\n<p>The destrachan can't use Painful Harmonics again for [[/br 1d4 #Recharge Painful Harmonics]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Deafened]{Deafened} for 3 rounds and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is deafened for 1 minute and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 3}.</p>"
